            <li><strong>Vertical Sidebar</strong> - perfect for dashboards and admin interfaces</li>
            <li><strong>Hover Effects</strong> - v12.0 Spring physics on all interactions</li>
            <li><strong>Mobile Ready</strong> - responsive behavior on all breakpoints</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3 mt-6 text-text-primary">Animation Details</h3>
          <ul class="list">
            <li><strong>Dropdowns</strong> - fade in with translateY slide using Spring easing</li>
            <li><strong>Icons</strong> - rotate 180° on parent hover for dropdown indicators</li>
            <li><strong>Links</strong> - subtle translateX on hover for visual feedback</li>
            <li><strong>Mega Menu</strong> - smooth fade and slide from top</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3 mt-6 text-text-primary">Accessibility</h3>
          <ul class="list">
            <li><strong>Keyboard Navigation</strong> - full support for tab and arrow keys</li>
            <li><strong>Focus States</strong> - visible focus indicators on all interactive elements</li>
            <li><strong>ARIA Labels</strong> - semantic HTML with proper roles and labels</li>
            <li><strong>Screen Readers</strong> - descriptive text for all navigation elements</li>
          </ul>
